<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ヘルプ</title>
  <script src="/js/tailwindcss.js"></script>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-900 text-white font-sans">
    <header class="bg-gray-800 flex p-4 justify-between items-center top-0 left-0 w-full z-10">
        <form action="/wkt/s" method="get" class="w-1/2" id="searchForm">
            <input type="text" name="q" id="searchbox" placeholder="検索" class="searchbox w-full p-2 rounded bg-gray-700 text-white">
        </form>
        <nav class="space-x-4">
            <a href="/wkt" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white">ホーム</a>
            <a href="/wkt/trend" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white">トレンド</a>
            <a href="/wkt/cl/history" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white">履歴</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-12 px-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">ヘルプページ</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-400 text-lg mb-8">
      なんか、ヘルプ的な。使い方を書いてるよ。
    </p>
  <div class="mt-6">
      <input type="text" id="search" placeholder="ヘルプを検索..." class="w-full max-w-md p-2 border rounded-lg shadow-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 text-black">
  </div>
  
    
    <div class="space-y-4" id="app-list">
      <div class="faq-item bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <button class="faq-btn w-full text-left px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center text-lg font-medium text-gray-200 hover:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500">
          <span class="faq-title"></span>
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 transform transition-transform duration-200 faq-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content px-6 py-4 hidden bg-gray-700 text-gray-300">
          <p>このサイトはシンプルで効率的に情報を取得できるよう設計されています。ユーザーが直感的に操作できるUI/UXを提供します。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <button class="faq-btn w-full text-left px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center text-lg font-medium text-gray-200 hover:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500">
          <span class="faq-title">利用方法について</span>
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 transform transition-transform duration-200 faq-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content px-6 py-4 hidden bg-gray-700 text-gray-300">
          <p>サイトの利用は非常に簡単です。トップページからすぐに目的の情報を検索でき、インターフェースも非常に直感的です。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <button class="faq-btn w-full text-left px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center text-lg font-medium text-gray-200 hover:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500">
          <span class="faq-title">サポートについて</span>
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 transform transition-transform duration-200 faq-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content px-6 py-4 hidden bg-gray-700 text-gray-300">
          <p>サポートは24/7体制で対応しており、どんな疑問にもすぐにお答えできるようになっています。詳細はサポートページをご覧ください。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
      $('.faq-btn').click(function() {
        const content = $(this).next('.faq-content');
        const icon = $(this).find('.faq-icon');
        content.toggleClass('hidden');
        icon.toggleClass('rotate-180');
      });
    });
    const searchInput = document.getElementById('search');
    const toolList = document.getElementById('app-list');
    const tools = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');

    searchInput.addEventListener('input', function() {
        const searchText = searchInput.value.toLowerCase();
        tools.forEach(tool => {
            const title = tool.querySelector('.faq-title').textContent.toLowerCase();
            const description = tool.querySelector('.faq-content').textContent.toLowerCase();
            if (title.includes(searchText) || description.includes(searchText)) {
                tool.style.display = '';
            } else {
                tool.style.display = 'none';
            }
        });
    });
  </script>

</body>
</html>
